parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission False Neutral and Slipping Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission false neutral and slipping issues can cause the motorcycle to suddenly lose power, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of gear
false neutrals occur
especially between 2nd and 3rd gear
and the motorcycle may downshift unexpectedly. The symptoms may worsen over time
leading to more frequent occurrences.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and gearbox can cause the motorcycle to lose power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the motorcycle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump replacement recall to address the underlying issue can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience to the driver.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls or fails to start
fuel pump malfunction
recall repair did not resolve the issue
issue emerged after recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed Fuel Pump Replacement Recall Repair
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in obtaining the necessary parts for the fuel pump replacement recall can leave the vehicle in an unsafe condition, exposing the driver to potential risks.
symptoms: Delay in obtaining recall repair parts
dealer unable to perform recall repair
recall repair not completed despite part availability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear wheel bearing can cause the rear wheel to lock up, leading to loss of control of the motorcycle, which can result in accidents, injuries, and even death.
symptoms: Rear wheel spins or locks up
wheel damage
unusual noise or vibration from the rear wheel
difficulty controlling the motorcycle.
